  "texts": [
    "Xiao (2010) found a significantly greater mean sentence length in translated Chinese than in native Chinese.",
    "However, Xiao and Yue (2009) found the difference in mean sentence length between the two text types was not statistically significant.",
    "To sum up, there is still no conclusive evidence for a reduction in mean sentence length and, thus, simplification of translational language.",
    "More recent studies also used some other syntactic features to test the simplification universal.",
    "For example, Liu and Afzaal (2021) examined syntactic complexity in translated English and English original texts."
  ],
